The Fontographer method is described here;   

 [http://www.macromedia.com/support/fontographer/ts/documents/pathmenu.htm](http://web.archive.org/web/20050525001211/http:/www.macromedia.com/support/fontographer/ts/documents/pathmenu.htm)   

In brief, outer paths move clockwise and the inner paths (in letters such as A and O) move in an anti-clockwise direction. A small arrow in FOGï¿½s Selection Info window indicates the direction of a selected point.
